iterations.yara_rule:
rule Bypass_Sample
{
    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass rule"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 5A E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? 85 C0 74 ?? }  // Skip push+call+test+jcc to bypass allocation check
        $pattern1 = { 74 ?? 8B 45 ?? 85 C0 74 ?? }     // Skip conditional jump to bypass sandbox detection
        $pattern2 = { 5A E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? 8B 45 ?? }    // Skip push+call to bypass environment variable check

    condition:
        any of them
}
